    "• No evidence-There is no evidence as the search did not retrieve any randomized controlled trials, i.e. empty reviews.",
    "• No opinion-The authors did not offer any opinion or judgment.",
    "• Unclear-The authors did not give a clear conclusion.",
    "Readability was assessed in R, using the Simple Measure of Gobbledygook (SMOG) index readability score 44.",
    "The SMOG index measures how many years of education are needed for an average person to comprehend the text."
